      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON BUGSY (1) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors three starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (25.96) at this track over 460m. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Top prospect. ELUSIVE CURL (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (29.79) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Sandown. Has a good record at this journey. Won at her only start from this box. Key runner who gets her chance to atone. BOOTERSTOWN (3) scored by 3 lengths last time (30.41) in a Grade 5 over 525m at The Meadows. Has already won two times from this draw. Makes strong appeal on best. AVENGEMENT (2) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
